.SH Name
.SP 5 5
add_respond_command -  This method adds a responable command set of values to the living object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void add_respond_command(string type,
object ob,
mixed data)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the type of thing to set as a response
%^BOLD%^ob%^RESET%^ - the object which is giving us the thing
%^BOLD%^data%^RESET%^ - the data associated with the command

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/respond_cmd.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method adds a responable command set of values to the
living object.
